Keyboard shortcuts:

	Global:
x	g then d - All discussions
x	g then f - Followed discussions
x	g then F - Favourite discussions
x	g then c - Categories
x	g then u - Users
x	g then i - Invites
x	g then m - Messages
x	Shift+j/k or n/p - Next/previous page

	Discussions or conversations list:
x	j/k and n/p - Next/previous item
x	o/enter - Open discussion (Hold shift to open in new tab)
x	m/y - Mark as read
	r - Refresh list
x	c - New discussion
	
	Viewing posts and messages:
x	j/k and n/p - Next/previous post
x	c - Go to compose reply
x	u - Go back to list

	Viewing posts:
x	q - Quote post
x	r - Load new posts


Old B3S config:

# Name of forum
forum_name: BUTT3RSCOTCH
# Short version of forum name (for use on iPhone etc)
forum_short_name: B3S
# HTML formatted version of forum_name
forum_title: BUTT<em>3</em>RSCOTCH

default_domain: butt3rscotch.org
asset_host: http://assets%d.butt3rscotch.org
mail_sender: Butt3rscotch <noreply@butt3rscotch.org>
session_key: _butt3rscotch_session

# Themes
default_theme: b3s
default_iphone_theme: b3s

# Enter your API key to enable Flickr integration:
flickr_api: 016918184821edf95505d9acd61e64c4

# Google API key
google_analytics: UA-8897656-1

# Enable Xbox Live integration
xbox_live_enabled: true

# == PERMISSIONS ==

# Enable public browsing
public_browsing: false

# Enable signups. The invites system will be enabled if this is set to false.
signups_allowed: false

# Signups must be approved by a user admin
signup_approval_required: false
